{"tid":2246763,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"面同背隻生暗瘡做食物測試","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T18:16:29.000Z","uid":91355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"681785d24d649a1a646bd6f836b9bd9325a186e4","tid":2246763,"uid":91355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"有無人做過食物測試可以分享下個流程/價錢係點<br />\n<br />\n我塊面、背隻、手臂都keep住有暗瘡生出黎, 由中學開始已經係咁, 差唔多十幾年, 好似斷唔到咁, 留左好多印係到<br />\n<br />\n覺得好似點做外部清潔都好, 都係無咩用, 都係會keep住生瘡出黎<br />\n<br />\n想做食物測試搵番個致敏源出黎, 睇下自己有咩要戎口, 減輕生瘡既情況<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家"},{"pid":"6316d8d202f138a4bd915872cc82514955d87902","tid":2246763,"uid":293097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"試下戒 堅果 奶製品（芝士 奶） 咖啡 麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f3de3acfa9542bc5e21c0d36dd7a5f958d6649","tid":2246763,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗唔該<br />\n想做咪去做，你上嚟都係想聽人賣下廣告，咁不如你直接踩上去聽佢賣啦"},{"pid":"98f05063f642e78451f4510218be1b49b17cb7ba","tid":2246763,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"快啲做<br />\n致敏好易引起暗瘡<br />\n底過你買護膚品"},{"pid":"2eab63efec5f762ee1e29a53559fac668291ded2","tid":2246763,"uid":91355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6316d8d202f138a4bd915872cc82514955d87902","tid":2246763,"uid":293097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"試下戒 堅果 奶製品（芝士 奶） 咖啡 麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"依家戒口好似好盲目咁戒, 好似搵唔到致敏源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52380d78ea6b4322ad3ad6dc9ebf69da2dc1c14d","tid":2246763,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"我一做gym飲蛋白粉背脊就會有 之前停左做半年gym完全冇"},{"pid":"4f5bf643cf1913a164ce12699dd2